      <scopecontent id="aspace_a4a02774a93b8ba2a97eb6517acc6150">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection is comprised of photographs used in We Minded the Store Yale Life and Letters During World War II (1975) by Polly S. Buck. The photographs depict student life in Branford College, Yale University, during the years 1944-1946, a large majority of which are of the Navy ROTC. The collection also includes photographs of individual students and clippings.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_83e7ed10ea9f04c4b721f25d3360a628">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged by alphabetically by date.</p>  
      </arrangement>
